  "comment": "LED PAR 60X3W WW: A modern alternative to traditional PAR 64 cans, the PAR 300 WW delivers rich, warm white illumination with precision and consistency. Equipped with 60 x 3W warm white LEDs, it offers an elegant blend of performance and efficiency—ideal for face lighting, theaters, and ambient applications.\n\nIts rugged die-cast aluminum housing and powerful heat sink ensure long-lasting reliability. With multiple beam angle options and support for 4CH / 8CH DMX modes, it adapts effortlessly to diverse professional setups.\n\nFrom subtle warmth to bold highlights, the PAR 300 WW lights every moment with timeless charm.\n\n",
